<view class="container">
  <image src="http://localhost:5001/images/recipe/06.jpg" class="recipe-image" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="recipe-info">
    <text class="recipe-title">手抓羊排</text>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">所需食材</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ing-list">
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">葱</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">姜</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">蒜</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">花椒</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">盐</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">醋</text></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">烹饪步骤</text>
      </view>
      <view class="step-list">
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>1</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">取出羊排，用清水浸泡 15 分钟，沥干。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>2</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">锅内放入凉水和羊排一起下锅，烧开后撇去浮沫，放入葱、姜、盐、花椒，中小火煮一个半小时即可。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>3</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">取小碗加入蒜泥与醋调成蘸料，搭配食用。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>